{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-talk-about-past-experiences/task-11","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-how-to-talk-about-past-experiences","challengeType":19,"description":"","nodules":null,"explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p>James koristi reč <span class=\"highlighted-text\">nothing</span>, koja ukazuje na nepostojanje bilo kakvog otkrića. Primer:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">She found nothing unusual in the report.</span> - Izveštaj je imao standardne karakteristike.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">We saw nothing strange during the test.</span> - Bilo je veoma uobičajen ispit.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Nasuprot tome, u negativnoj rečenici, koristićete <span class=\"highlighted-text\">anything</span> umesto <span class=\"highlighted-text\">nothing</span>. Na primer:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Potvrda: <span class=\"highlighted-text\">He found nothing.</span> - Nije bilo otkrića.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Greška: <span class=\"highlighted-text\">He didn't find anything.</span> - Nije pronađen nijedan rezultat.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Primećujete da, u negativnim rečenicama i pitanjima sa <span class=\"highlighted-text\">did</span>, glavni glagol (u ovom slučaju, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">find</span>) je u svojoj osnovnoj formi. Pomoćni glagol <span class=\"highlighted-text\">did</span> je onaj koji pokazuje da je ova rečenica u prošlom vremenu. Primer:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">They didn't find anything wrong with the program.</span> - Pronaći bilo šta je bila stvar prošlosti.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">I didn't see anything unusual during the presentation.</span> - Nije bilo ništa neobično viđeno na izložbama koje su se desile ranije.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Ova struktura pomaže da se izbegnu negativne reči dva puta. Odgovor Džejmsa, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Nothing at first</span>, pokazuje pozitivnu rečenicu koja naglašava da nije mogao ništa pronaći kada je počeo da pretražuje.</p>\n</section>","helpCategory":"English","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušajte audio odgovor na pitanje ispod.</p>\n</section>","fields":{"slug":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-talk-about-past-experiences/task-11"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Šta je James otkrio na početku?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p>Nije ništa otkrio/otkrila.</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Otkrio je nešto.</p>","feedback":"<p>Usemi James kaže da ne vidiš da je pronašao nešto.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Pronašao je sve odjednom.</p>","feedback":"<p>Što James kaže protivreči ideji da je sve pronašao.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Neću ništa tražiti.</p>","feedback":"<p>Zapravo je nešto tražio.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":1}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"interview-room3.png","characters":[{"character":"Lisa","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.2},"opacity":0},{"character":"James","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.2},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"B1_2-1.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":8.86,"finishTimestamp":11.04},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Lisa","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Lisa","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":2,"dialogue":{"text":"What did you find there?","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Lisa","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":2.14,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"James","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":2.14,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"James","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":2.28,"finishTime":3.18,"dialogue":{"text":"Nothing at first.","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"ch